the actions of your group were uncalled for unless they in turn offered to duel EVERY person that they wronged in EVERY instance. If they did that, I apologize, if not, well, the person who said 'Dood,...' was right.</P><P>I roleplay, but I will not do it at the expense of others entertainment, Roleplay may be a key word in the RPG format, but so is Game.</P><P></P><P><BR>Beeker Rosethorn<BR>Loving Husband to Dawna<BR>&lt;Spirit of the Moon&gt;<BR>Innoruuk Server</font></td></tr><tr><td bgcolor='#6F6559' valign="top"><font color='#ffffff' face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica' size='2'>Beeker</font></td><td bgcolor='#6F6559'  valign='top' ><font color='#ffffff' face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica' size='1'>Posted - 3 November 2000 5:40 PST</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="Javascript:openWindow('profile.asp?mode=display&id=21145')"><img src='profile.gif' alt='Show Profile' border=0 align='absmiddle' hspace=6></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href='mail.asp?id=21145'><img src='email.gif' alt='Email Poster' border=0 align='absmiddle' hspace=6></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href='post.asp?method=edit&reply_id=139953&auth=21145&forum_title=EQ+Tavern&topic_title=Comments%3A+%28PHOF%29+%2D+Not+an+RPG&forum_id=1315&topic_id=28807'><img src='edit.gif' alt='Edit Message' border=0 align='absmiddle' hspace=6></a><hr noshade size=1><font color='#ffffff' face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica' size='2'>Stupid bugs. Kept saying my post contained no data, so I hit the send button again.</P><P></P><P>Beeker Rosethorn<BR>Loving Husband to Dawna<BR>&lt;Spirit of the Moon&gt;<BR>Innoruuk Server</P><P>Edited by - Beeker on 11/3/2000 5:46:59 AM</font></td></tr><tr><td bgcolor='#6F6559' valign="top"><font color='#ffffff' face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica' size='2'>Beeker</font></td><td bgcolor='#6F6559'  valign='top' ><font color='#ffffff' face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica' size='1'>Posted - 3 November 2000 5:41 PST</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="Javascript:openWindow('profile.asp?mode=display&id=21145')"><img src='profile.gif' alt='Show Profile